Make project minutes models

Source: R/fn_make.R
make_project_minutes_mdls.Rd

make_project_minutes_mdls() is a Make function that creates a new R object. Specifically, this function implements an algorithm to make project minutes models. The function returns Tpm models (a list).

Usage

make_project_minutes_mdls(
  X_Ready4useDyad,
  family_2_1L_chr = "Gamma(link = 'inverse')",
  link_1_1L_chr = "logit",
  x_part_1_ls = NULL,
  x_part_2_ls = NULL,
  y_1L_chr = "Minutes_change",
  ...
)

Arguments

X_Ready4useDyad

PARAM_DESCRIPTION

family_2_1L_chr

Family 2 (a character vector of length one), Default: 'Gamma(link = 'inverse')'

link_1_1L_chr

Link 1 (a character vector of length one), Default: 'logit'

x_part_1_ls

X part 1 (a list), Default: NULL

x_part_2_ls

X part 2 (a list), Default: NULL

y_1L_chr

Y (a character vector of length one), Default: 'Minutes_change'

...

Additional arguments

Value

Tpm models (a list)
